{"tid":818111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"詹sir教防漏水： 靠牛皮膠紙　保鮮紙","createTime":"2018-09-14T01:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T05:27:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d75a58cfdd3b92b9a4500bcbe77c7dc3c8671a97","tid":818111,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T01:18:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180914/20499276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F20499276&d=AAikRAnnkpmqLFbgyV%2BMLMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=29b39f95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F20499276&h=74645fc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180914/20499276</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月14日 <br />\n<br />\n詹sir教防漏水：<br />\n靠牛皮膠紙　保鮮紙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180914/large/14la2p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180914%2Flarge%2F14la2p05.jpg&h=8e9560d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n驗樓師詹sir建議用牛皮膠紙在玻璃上貼「井」字，防爆裂時裂紋擴大。溫瑞麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】超強颱風「山竹」逼近，市民如臨大敵，不少市民提早做好防風防漏水措施。要防止住所窗門漏水，並不需要花費大量金錢，只需常備兩大法寶：牛皮膠紙及保鮮紙。<br />\n<br />\n驗樓師詹濟南「詹sir」教路，風季來臨前要檢查窗邊會否漏風，「會漏風即係會漏水」，方法很簡單，只需關閉所有門窗，開啟風扇及冷氣機，造成空氣流動，將手置於窗邊，若能感覺有風吹入，即是漏風。惟颱風將近，即使發現漏風亦來不及補救，詹sir醒你5大貼士：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180914/large/a0204a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180914%2Flarge%2Fa0204a.gif&h=828e2453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冷氣機屬漏水高危位，詹稱在底部貼上牛皮膠紙（小圖）便可解決。<br />\n<br />\n玻璃貼「井」字 保鮮紙揳窗<br />\n<br />\n窗邊：若窗邊與窗框有空隙，大雨時必滲水，只需將保鮮紙捲成條狀，放於空隙處，再把窗關上，由於保鮮紙不吸水，不用經常更換，亦可避免毛巾索水後滲入屋的情況，既經濟又方便。若滲水來自牆身，則只能放置毛巾吸水，待颱風過後於外牆油上防水漆。由於玻璃中心點是最脆弱部份，可以牛皮膠紙貼上「井」字，玻璃一旦爆裂，可防止裂紋擴大。之後可以白電油抹走玻璃上膠紙迹。<br />\n<br />\n冷氣機位：冷氣機四邊的防水膠不夠或老化，大雨時會漏水，其中底部更高危；只需於漏水位置貼上牛皮膠紙，問題便解決。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180914/large/a0204b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180914%2Flarge%2Fa0204b.gif&h=0c0123b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n抽氣扇位：市面上的抽氣扇，大部份於向外位置設有擋板，簡單地將檔板放下便可避免入水。<br />\n<br />\n抽油煙機：出風口應明顯向下，否則雨水會沿喉管流入屋，最佳方法是不使用出風喉管，勤換機內過濾器。<br />\n<br />\n露台趟門：兩邊趟門中間的接合位置屬入水高危，可以牛皮膠紙將接合位置封起。<br />\n<br />\n另外，大雨過後窗口式冷氣去水喉經常遭沙石堵塞，詹sir提醒，冷氣低盤面積應比冷氣機身小，以免外露部份盛載沙石或垃圾。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n風力或超港珠澳橋承受上限<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n西九站料關閉　高鐵員工照上班無補水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杏花邨車場設抽水泵戒備<br />\n<br />\n司機駛走地下車場座駕市民掃水　商戶防洪　澳門全民戒備<br />\n<br />\n襲台風險低　廣東高危<br />\n<br />\n風力或超港珠澳橋承受上限<br />\n<br />\n西九站料關閉高鐵員工照上班無補水<br />\n<br />\n天文台：山竹西移　威力不減後日吹10級暴風"},{"pid":"eb1627d982c92b8802d9988c9fb37a3d96fd1ebc","tid":818111,"uid":64858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T01:23:38.000Z","msg":"岩岩上佢驗樓班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd05972c49cdfea0359ea951d5ed0e876c4af004","tid":818111,"uid":83102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T01:29:42.000Z","msg":"係地盤見佢短牛仔褲+紅色polo<br />\n想比人屌屎忽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d256c9620cf2f1cf71a3b5f1bea27d92ac25b907","tid":818111,"uid":78632,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T01:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/pl2qwr76ujky.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fpl2qwr76ujky.png&h=9677b9f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1eac66ba671a78abba0a1af2f28c62233ea46b30","tid":818111,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd05972c49cdfea0359ea951d5ed0e876c4af004","tid":818111,"uid":83102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T01:29:42.000Z","msg":"係地盤見佢短牛仔褲+紅色polo<br />\n想比人屌屎忽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf52e51f95d2e4e5c7ef193b82cb3d5bc845c25","tid":818111,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:19:01.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔明點貼"},{"pid":"dc88deae7fec24c289bf2ab59ec42e577a3cdeb6","tid":818111,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:17:09.000Z","msg":"米 X 井字型<br />\n邊隻最有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c979064824ec6c09eb20b4bc7a6f6aa50d7b0139","tid":818111,"uid":191443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"條友都係呃飯食"},{"pid":"fe5cef769c7b84fdbda2c4716d80962a2f0569ab","tid":818111,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c979064824ec6c09eb20b4bc7a6f6aa50d7b0139","tid":818111,"uid":191443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"條友都係呃飯食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"舉例先, 冇就收皮"},{"pid":"5f144085e92cdb6bcd03ddc3f98c457020fad040","tid":818111,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}